reviewText: Really old and boring info. Try Thrift Store Prospecting by Rose Morgan and really uncover those hidden treasures. Unfortunately book must be ordered direct from auther and is therefore expensive.

Original pilot episode to TRAVEL CHANNEL's series called CASH & TREASURES -- now called "Treasure Hunter: Kirsten Gum".  Lots of great locations you can visit and keep whatever you find!  Very entertaining and fun show.
